Additional Notice (Educational Materials)

This repository includes instructional materials (such as notebooks, documentation, and teaching resources) developed to support programming education.

These materials are intended to be used as Open Educational Resources (OER) to support:
- broad dissemination
- institutional adoption
- equitable access to foundational programming education
- adaptation across diverse learning environments

Users are encouraged to reuse and adapt these materials for educational purposes, with appropriate attribution.
